{"id":296820179,"lang":"python3","time":"1 year, 11 months","timestamp":1579803149,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"44 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/296820179/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Divide Two Integers","memory":"12.7 MB","code":"class Solution:\n    def divide(self, dividend: int, divisor: int) -> int:\n        toggle = -1 if (divisor > 0 and dividend < 0) or (divisor < 0 and dividend > 0) else 1\n        dividend, divisor = abs(dividend), abs(divisor)\n        q, times = 0, 0\n        while dividend >= divisor:\n            temp = dividend - (divisor << times)\n            if temp >= 0:\n                q += (1 << times)\n                times += 1\n                dividend = temp\n            else:\n                times -= 1\n        return max(-2147483648, min(q * toggle, 2147483647))","compare_result":"","title_slug":"divide-two-integers"}
